{"tid":1479053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持下去，並不是香港人真的足夠堅強，而是我們別無選擇。","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T18:04:48.000Z","uid":307857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b645c56000a4028f0685c5f79b634a813497c92","tid":1479053,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtOLaDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtOLaDq.jpg&h=34e2d5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堅持下去，並不是香港人真的足夠堅強，而是我們別無選擇。 - 邱吉爾, 2019<br />\n<br />\n二零一九年，只是二戰世界大戰的延續，自由和黑暗勢力的對決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120826/large/26ls9p3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120826%2Flarge%2F26ls9p3n.jpg&h=4dd74ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還記得在同一片土地上為香港抵抗黑暗到來的一萬三千名士兵?<br />\n「八十年代這麼多香港人移民加拿大，有多少人知道二千名加拿大士兵送到香港當炮灰？香港人對歷史沒有甚麼感覺。」<br />\n重光紀念日取消後，香港人慢慢忘掉幾十年前淪陷的三年零八個月。<br />\n<br />\n由於土生土長的香港人當時沒有激烈抵抗，更有一些賤民向極權政府投懷送抱。<br />\n自一九九七年七月一日起，香港已淪陷到極權政府手上二十八年。<br />\n香港淪陷期間完全「制度崩壞」。<br />\n現正在經歷香港淪陷的人，不少人說曾看過黨衛軍毆打、就地處決香港市民 ── 起因往往都是小事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190814/s00006/7a88f430d5f4a7413366d31f9f04644e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190814%2Fs00006%2F7a88f430d5f4a7413366d31f9f04644e.jpg&h=03a6725e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QdD2ivUSL-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQdD2ivUSL-A&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75dAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=ccfd6724\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QdD2ivUSL-A</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人對歷史認識不足，亦不清楚歷史如何影響著香港的軌跡。不識歷史，又如何了解自由得來不易？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L90BCEVH41U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL90BCEVH41U&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75dAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=cbbad188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L90BCEVH41U</a>"},{"pid":"32105d3e791de98529b6989f3a6c6cc0d428b4b3","tid":1479053,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"別無選擇，唯有攬炒！<br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}